> Entertainment CBS drama 'Code Black' welcomes cast from 'The Lion King' In this image released by CBS, Marcia Gay Harden, from left, Melanie Chandra and Alton Fitzgerald White appear in a scene from the series "Code Black." scheduled to air on Nov. 25, 2015 on CBS. White, who has played the role of “Mufasa” in “The Lion King” over 4000 times, guest stars. (Monty Brinton/CBS via AP) 
